profile_positions.description:
Set-up and execution of solutions for customers regarding:
- Risk management functions and risk governance;
- Internal Control framework and Business assurance;
- Internal audit plans, managing and conducting operational audits, IT audits and project audits.
- Operational Risk Management, Asset Risk Management, Enterprise Risk Management, Credit Risk Management.

Responsible for complex projects in the areas of design, improvement and implementation of risk management and operational auditing. Coaching and training (junior and medior) risk consultants. Member core team audit & risk.

Successful projects conducted and supervised within various sectors:
- Banking (online, savings, mortgages, investments);
- (International) insurance;
- Housing Associations;
- Government (ministries, defence, police).
